== The 2-Week Rapid Relief Protocol
<sec:two-week-protocol>

This protocol targets the six most disabling symptom domains with interventions that can be initiated immediately. The goal is to reduce overall suffering from 9/10 severity to 4–5/10 within 14 days, making the condition bearable. For Global/Advanced subtype patients, prioritize implementing the symptom domains most affecting you (see Section @sec:subtype-assessment) rather than trying all protocols simultaneously on day 1.

